## Observability & Testing Strategy

**Logged on every request:** request_id, user_id (when known), route, status, duration, and the structured event.

**Metrics exported:** {{METRICS_LIST}}

**Testing model:**

| Layer | What we run | Mocked or live | When |
|-------|-------------|----------------|------|
| Unit | `pnpm test` | Mocked vendors | Pre-commit |
| Live integration | `pnpm test:live` | Live vendors (gated on secret presence) | CI nightly |
| API smoke | `pnpm test:api` | Spins up built app | CI on every push |
| E2E | `pnpm test:e2e` | Playwright against dev server | CI nightly |
| Observability | `/api/observability/health` | Live | On deploy + doctor |

